ason%203%20to%20fan-favourite%20K-drama%20%E2%80%98Yumi%E2%80%99s%20Cells%E2%80%99%20Season%203%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20a%20curated%20list%20of%20the%20hottest%20releases%20on%20OTT%20this%20week.%E2%80%98Euphoria%20Season%203'The%20new%20season%20of%20%E2%80%98Euphoria%E2%80%99%20shifts%20the%20storyline%20from%20high%20school%20to%20a%20significant%20five-year%20time%20jump%20into%20adulthood.%20Most%20of%20the%20core%20cast%20returns%20for%20the%20season%2C%20including%20Zendaya%2C%20Sydney%20Sweeney%2C%20Hunter%20Schafer%2C%20Jacob%20Elordi%2C%20Alexa%20Demie%2C%20and%20Maude%20Apatow.Created%20and%20directed%20by%20Sam%20Levinson%2C%20%E2%80%98Euphoria%E2%80%99%20Season%201%20premiered%20in%202019%20and%20Season%202%20premiered%20in%202022.%20The%20first%20episode%20premieres%20Sunday%2C%20April%2012%2C%20on%20HBO%20Max%20in%20the%20US.%20Since%20international%20premiere%20time%20varies%20by%20region%2C%20the%20episode%20will%20drop%20on%2013th%20April%20in%20India.%20The%20season%20will%20consist%20of%20eight%20episodes%2C%20with%20new%20installments%20dropping%20weekly%20on%20Sundays%20through%20May%2031%2C%202026.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cameron%20Diaz%20reveals%20THIS%20strict%20house%20rule%20for%20guests%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775977260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-130203968%2Cimgsize-43212.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fenglish%2Fcameron-diaz-reveals-strict-house-rule-that-leaves-guests-waiting-outside-street-shoes-no-entry%2Farticleshow%2F130203953.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F130203953.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ECameron%20Diaz%20enforces%20