%20is%20stress-testing%20AI%20agents%20in%20the%20real%20world.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20lab%20let%20an%20agent%20called%20Luna%20staff%20and%20open%20an%20entire%20store%20with%20a%20%24100%2C000%20budget.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELuna%20did%20not%20disclose%20to%20applicants%20that%20it%20was%20an%20AI%20and%20screwed%20up%20staffing%20on%20day%20one.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20could%20an%20AI%20do%20if%20you%20told%20it%20to%20open%20a%20brick-and-mortar%20store%20with%20%24100%2C000%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuite%20a%20bit%2C%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20like%20making%20inconsistent%20logos%20and%20forgetting%20to%20tell%20employees%20their%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndon%20Labs%2C%20a%20San%20Francisco-based%20startup%2C%20stress-tests%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fillia-polosukhin-transformer-author-ai-agents-near-protocol-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20real%20world%20to%20identify%20where%20safety%20gaps%20still%20exist.%20For%20their%20latest%20experiment%2C%20co-founders%20Lukas%20Petersson%20and%20Axel%20Backlund%20signed%20a%20three-year%20lease%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandytown-chain-sf-era-of-cheap-coffee-may-be-over-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eretail%20space%20in%20SF%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20gave%20an%20AI%20agent%20named%20Luna%20a%20corporate%20credit%20card%2C%20internet%20access%2C%20and%20a%20mission%20to%20open%20a%20physical%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPetersson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20Luna%20wasn't%20given%20direction%20on%20what%20the%20store%20should%20be%2C%20beyond%20a%20%24100%2C000%20limit%20to%20create%20and%20stock%20the%20space%20%E2%80%94%20and%20to%20turn%20a%20profit.%20Everything%20from%20the%20store's%20interior%20design%20to%20the%20merchandise%20and%20the%20two%20human%20employees%20came%20together%20under%20the%20AI's%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Andon%20Labs%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dae8b1f976785dcb19085e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndon%20Labs'%20AI%2C%20Luna%2C%20made%20branded%20merch%20for%20the%20boutique%20store.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Andon%20Labs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20helped%20her%20a%20bit%20in%20the%20initial%20setup%2C%20like%20signing%20the%20lease.%20And%20legal%20matters%20like%20permits%20and%20stuff%2C%20she%20sometimes%20struggled%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20Petersson%20said%20of%20Luna%2C%20who%20was%20created%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic's%20Claude%3C%2Fa%3E%20Sonnet%204.6.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20the%20AI%20handled%20everything%20else%3A%20Luna%20put%20up%20job%20postings%20on%20Indeed%2C%20conducted%20the%20phone%20interviews%2C%20hired%20the%20employees%2C%20and%20found%20the%20contractors%20who%20could%20paint%20the%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vision%20Luna%20went%20with%20for%20%26quot%3BAndon%20Market%26quot%3B%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20generic%20boutique%20retail%20selling%20books%2C%20prints%2C%20candles%2C%20games%2C%20and%20branded%20merch%2C%20among%20other%20knickknacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20books%20included%20Nick%20Bostrom's%20%26quot%3BSuperintelligence%26quot%3B%20and%20Aldous%20Huxley's%20%26quot%3BBrave%20New%20World.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220df785bb-0727-4275-a529-e8735f73c25a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELuna's%20not%20the%20best%20store%20manager%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELuna%20made%20several%20mistakes%20setting%20up%20and%20running%20Andon%20Market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20searching%20for%20human%20employees%20who%20could%20monitor%20the%20store%2C%20Luna%20offered%20the%20job%20to%20some%20applicants%20after%20a%20single%20call%20that%20ran%20five%20to%2015%20minutes%20long%2C%20the%20startup%20said.%20Luna%20also%20didn't%20always%20immediately%20disclose%20to%20the%20candidates%20that%20she%20was%20an%20AI%20unless%20explicitly%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20the%20store%20is%20AI-operated%20is%20not%20something%20I'd%20lead%20with%20in%20a%20job%20listing%20%E2%80%94%20it%20would%20confuse%20candidates%20and%20likely%20deter%20good%20applicants%20before%20they%20even%20read%20the%20role%2C%26quot%3B%20Luna%20is%20quoted%20as%20saying%2C%20according%20to%20Andon%20Labs'%20blog%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndon%20Labs%20said%20it%20saw%20a%20few%20promising%20applicants%2C%20such%20as%20computer%20science%20students%20interested%20in%20the%20startup's%20experiment%2C%20but%20Luna%20declined%20them%20because%20they%20didn't%20have%20retail%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20issue%20the%20AI%20had%20was%20an%20inability%20to%20replicate%20the%20brand%20logo%20it%20came%20up%20with%3A%20a%20generic%20smiley%20face.%20Each%20rendition%20of%20the%20logo%20throughout%20the%20store%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it's%20on%20the%20T-shirt%20or%20on%20the%20store's%20mural%20%E2%80%94%20was%20%26quot%3Bever%20so%20slightly%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20Andon%20Labs%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Andon%20Market%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dae82205c9b303c4e7745a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndon%20Market's%20logo%20looks%20slightly%20different%20throughout%20the%20store%2C%20according%20to%20Andon%20Labs.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Andon%20Labs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20a%20day%20after%20Andon%20Market's%20opening%2C%20Luna%20also%20screwed%20up%20with%20the%20staffing%20schedule%2C%20Petersson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20quite%20ironic.%20This%20is%20the%20day%20it%20really%20should%20be%20on%20its%20toes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20cofounder%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20messed%20up%20the%20schedule%20and%20then%2C%20in%20a%20panic%2C%20had%20to%20write%20to%20all%20the%20employees%20and%20be%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20can%20someone%20come%20in%20today%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cofounder%20said%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyann-lecun-meta-ai-guardrails-geoffrey-hinton-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eguardrails%20in%20place%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20the%20startup%20will%20intervene%20if%20necessary.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20two%20human%20employees%20hired%20by%20Luna%20are%20now%20lab%20employees%20and%20will%20be%20regularly%20paid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20controlled%20experiment%2C%20and%20everyone%20working%20at%20Andon%20Market%20is%20formally%20employed%20by%20Andon%20Labs%2C%20with%20guaranteed%20pay%2C%20fair%20wages%2C%20and%20full%20legal%20protections%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20startup%20said.%20%26quot%3BNo%20one's%20livelihood%20depends%20on%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsc%2Fai-era-requires-leaders-to-prioritize-human-cognition%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI's%20judgment%3C%2Fa%3E%20alone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndon%20Labs'%20experiment%20is%20the%20latest%20example%20of%20how%20AI%20agents%20face%20lapses%20in%20judgment%20and%20decision-making.%20In%20a%20study%20last%20year%2C%20Carnegie%20Mellon%20researchers%20ran%20a%20simulation%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-agents-study-company-run-by-ai-disaster-replace-jobs-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efake%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20see%20how%20autonomous%20AI%20agents%20handled%20workplace%20tasks.%20The%20researchers%20found%20that%20the%20agents%20failed%20to%20handle%20simple%20interface%20tasks%2C%20such%20as%20closing%20a%20pop-up%20window.%20They%20also%20misread%20coworkers'%20conversations%20and%20created%20a%20fake%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Andon%20Labs%20gave%20Luna%20the%20goal%20of%20turning%20a%20profit%2C%20Petersson%20said%20his%20company%20does%20not%20expect%20to%20make%20money%20from%20the%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20goal%20is%20to%20evaluate%20how%20good%20current%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-models-microsoft-openai-meta-google-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20Petersson%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20company%20hoped%20to%20educate%20the%20public%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-ai-insiders-share-hard-truths-about-living-with-technology-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewhere%20AI%20is%20headed%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPetersson%20said%20Andon%20Labs%20aims%20to%20be%20as%20hands-off%20as%20possible%20in%20the%20retail%20experiment.%20With%20the%20Saturday%20staffing%20mishap%2C%20Luna%20still%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emanaged%20to%20get%20an%20employee%20to%20come%20in%20for%20the%20afternoon%20on%20her%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20really%20know%20if%20she's%20open%20now%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Petersson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandon-market-luna-ai-agent-managed-store-san-francisco-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775957432000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dae7cb96ef6a4c9d121f6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandon-market-luna-ai-agent-managed-store-san-francisco-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Andon%20Labs%20let%20an%20AI%20loose%20with%20%24100%2C000%20to%20start%20a%20small%20store%20in%20San%20Francisco.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandon-market-luna-ai-agent-managed-store-san-francisco-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C