20like%20software%2C%20finance%2C%20and%20professional%20services.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20currently%20leads%20OpenAI%20in%20three%20specific%20sectors%3A%20information%2C%20finance%20and%20insurance%2C%20and%20personal%20services.%20Ramp's%20data%20only%20provides%20a%20snapshot%20of%20spending%20by%20that%20company's%20customers.%20However%2C%20it's%20a%20useful%20yardstick%20for%20how%20business%20adoption%20of%20AI%20is%20changing%20over%20time.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvancements%20in%20AI%20have%20begun%20to%20transform%20several%20industries.%20Major%20companies%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-push-employee-goals-tool-adoption-2-026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-internal-memo-using-ai-no-longer-optional-github-copilot-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvisa-says-its-burning-through-one-trillion-ai-tokens-month-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVisa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20encouraged%20employees%20to%20adopt%20the%20tech%20into%20their%20day-to-day%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ai-breakthrough-vibe-coding-revolution-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EClaude%20Code%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20a%20huge%20hit%20with%20software%20engineers%20and%20developers%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20one%20of%20the%20main%20drivers%20behind%20business%20spending%20on%20the%20startup's%20technology.%20The%20company%20also%20has%20top-performing%20models%2C%20according%20to%20benchmarking%20specialist%20Arena.ai.%20That%20likely%20influences%20which%20AI%20technology%20businesses%20choose.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20from%20Ramp%20showed%20that%20funding%20is%20a%20key%20predictor%20of%20whether%20a%20business%20adopts%20AI.%20VC-backed%20businesses%20have%20a%2080%25%20adoption%20rate%2C%20while%20companies%20backed%20by%20private-equity%20firms%20have%20a%2064%25%20adoption%20rate.%20Companies%20without%20either%20have%20a%2045%25%20adoption%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Ramp%20didn't%20provide%20a%20specific%20reason%20for%20Anthropic's%20surge%20among%20corporations%2C%20the%20company%20received%20an%20unexpected%20reputation%20boost%20in%20February%20when%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-ai-military-use-dario-amodei-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echallenged%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20Pentagon%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20month%2C%20Defense%20Secretary%20Pete%20Hegseth%20urged%20the%20company%20to%20agree%20with%20the%20military's%20terms%20of%20use%20for%20Claude%20or%20be%20blacklisted%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20refused%2C%20resulting%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-federal-agencies-stop-using-anthropic-technology-department-defense-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20telling%20federal%20agencies%20to%20stop%20using%20the%20tech%20and%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20designating%20Anthropic%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-blocks-anthropic-supply-chain-risk-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupply%20chain%20risk%3C%2Fa%3E.%20OpenAI%20stepped%20in%20to%20offer%20its%20services%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-ai-deal-sam-altman-pentagon-defense-department-anthropic-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20some%20users%20rallied%20around%20Anthropic.%20Claude%20temporarily%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-hits-number-one-app-store-openai-chatgpt-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurpassed%20ChatGPT%