3E%3Cli%3EAnthropic%20launched%20a%20beta%20version%20of%20Claude%20for%20Word.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20follows%20February's%20release%20of%20Claude%20add-ins%20for%20Excel%20and%20PowerPoint.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20AI%20startup's%20latest%20launch%20is%20partly%20aimed%20at%20legal%20professionals.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-mythos-cybersecurity-concerns-what-smart-people-are-saying-ai-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%20launched%20a%20beta%20version%20of%20Claude%20for%20Word%2C%20another%20challenge%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-microsoft-stocks-down-ai-replacement-future-of-software-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E's%20software%20empire%20and%20a%20bid%20to%20appeal%20more%20to%20the%20legal%20profession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20startup%2C%20having%20pushed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ai-software-claude-microsoft-powerpoint-excel-slack-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EClaude%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20Excel%20and%20PowerPoint%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20said%20its%20latest%20add-in%20for%20Word%20is%20%26quot%3Bdesigned%20for%20professionals%20who%20work%20extensively%20with%20documents%2C%20particularly%20in%20legal%20review%2C%20financial%20memo%20drafting%2C%20and%20iterative%20editing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20Anthropic%20said%20Claude%20for%20Word%20would%20allow%20users%20to%20ask%20questions%20about%20their%20documents%20and%20get%20answers%20with%20clickable%20section%20citations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20features%20include%20the%20ability%20to%20edit%20selected%20text%20while%20preserving%20surrounding%20styles%2C%20numbering%2C%20and%20formatting%2C%20while%20a%20%26quot%3Btracked%20changes%20mode%26quot%3B%20would%20allow%20users%20to%20accept%20or%20reject%20every%20edit%20as%20a%20revision%2C%20Anthropic%20explained.%3