n%20of%20her%20outstanding%20debt%20to%20Laurie%20remains%20unaddressed%20through%20the%20end%20of%20the%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaurie%20reappears%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7laIhWUshwc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteaser%20trailer%20for%20season%20three%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20delivering%20the%20line%2C%20%26quot%3BHello%2C%20Rue.%20You%20owe%20me%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a7aea620-bfb6-4914-a7b7-d99cd6ffc0a2%5C%22%3ELexi%20spends%20season%20two%20writing%20a%20play%20about%20her%20life%2C%20stirring%20up%20drama%20among%20her%20sister%20and%20friends.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maude%20Apatow%2C%20right%2C%20as%20Lexi%20in%20%26quot%3BEuphoria%26quot%3B%20season%20two.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cd77af6a864f6fcd7bc7bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMaude%20Apatow%2C%20right%2C%20as%20Lexi%20in%20%26quot%3BEuphoria%26quot%3B%20season%20two.%3Cp%3EEddy%20Chen%2FHBO%20Max%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20all%20the%20chaos%2C%20the%20show's%20perennial%20wallflower%20Lexi%20(Maude%20Apatow)%20decides%20to%20put%20her%20observational%20skills%20to%20good%20use.%20She%20writes%20and%20stars%20in%20a%20play%20called%20%26quot%3BOur%20Life%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20debuts%20in%20the%20penultimate%20episode%20of%20season%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELexi%20casts%20lookalike%20actors%20to%20portray%20her%20sister%2C%20Cassie%3B%20Cassie's%20best%20friend%2C%20Maddy%3B%20Maddy's%20best%20friend%2C%20Kat%20(Barbie%20Ferreira)%3B%20and%20Lexi's%20own%20best%20friend%2C%20Rue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELexi%20delights%20in%20the%20creativity%20and%20vulnerability%20of%20theater%2C%20although%20she%20frets%20about%20upsetting%20her%20sister%20and%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20after%20she%20observes%20that%20Cassie%20is%20experiencing%20some%20kind%20of%20nervous%20breakdown.%20She%20ultimately%20decides%20to%20go%20through%20with%20the%20play%20after%20consulting%20her%20new%20friend%2C%20Fezco%2C%20who%20sagely%20observes%2C%20%26quot%3BSome%20people%20need%20to%20get%20their%20feelings%20hurt%20sometimes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20play%20revisits%20significant%20moments%20in%20the%20fivesome's%20life%20through%20Lexi's%20personal%20lens%2C%20revealing%20her%20envy%20toward%20Cassie%2C%20her%20admiration%20of%20Maddy%2C%20and%20how%20she%20feels%20powerless%20in%20the%20face%20of%20Rue's%20addiction.%20Multiple%20scenes%20also%20depict%20the%20close%20bond%20between%20Cassie%20and%20Maddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20in%20the%20show's%20actual%20timeline%2C%20Maddy%20just%20found%20out%20that%20Cassie%20has%20been%20having%20sex%20with%20her%20ex-boyfriend%2C%20Nate%2C%20whom%20Maddy%20still%20loves%20%E2%80%94%20so%20the%20play%20stirs%20up%20some%20strong%20emotions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECassie%20tries%20to%20stop%20the%20play%20and%20undermine%20Lexi%20by%20running%20up%20onstage%2C%20and%20Maddy%20follows%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20physical%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20Rue%20says%20she%20loved%20her%20onstage%20portrayal%2C%20though%20she%20may%20be%20the%20only%20one.%20She%20even%20tells%20Lexi%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20your%20play%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20was%20able%20to%20look%20at%20my%20life%20and%20not%20hate%20myself%E2%80%A6%20Seeing%20it%20meant%20the%20world%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%20The%20lifelong%20friends%20end%20season%20two%20on%20good%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a3d2a57e-8af5-4c99-b808-f6ad091b9434%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20season%20two%20finale%2C%20Nate%20turns%20his%20father%20in%20to%20the%20police.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eric%20Dane%20as%20Cal%20Jacobs%20in%20%26quot%3BEuphoria%26quot%3B%20season%20two.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d53bcdf36fd1a78c051903%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEric%20Dane%20as%20Cal%20Jacobs%20in%20%26quot%3BEuphoria%26quot%3B%20season%20two.%3Cp%3EEddy%20Chen%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENate's%20troubled%20relationship%20with%20his%20father%2C%20Cal%20Jacobs%20(Eric%20Dane)%2C%20is%20a%20recurring%20theme%20throughout%20seasons%20one%20and%20two%20of%20%26quot%3BEuphoria.%26quot%3B%20As%20a%20child%2C%20Nate%20found%20self-filmed%20videos%20of%20Cal%20having%20encounters%20with%20gay%20men%2C%20queer%20women%2C%20and%20sex%20workers.%20In%20season%20one%2C%20we%20learn%20at%20least%20one%20person%20Cal%20filmed%20without%20her%20consent%20%E2%80%94%20Jules%20%E2%80%94%20was%20underage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECal%20finally%20opens%20up%20about%20his%20double%20life%20in%20season%20two%2C%20continuing%20to%20wreak%20emotional%20havoc%20on%20his%20wife%20and%20sons.%20Nate%20is%20particularly%20affected%2C%20living%20with%20constant%20fear%20that%20he%20takes%20after%20his%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20season%20two%20finale%2C%20Nate's%20fears%20and%20self-hatred%20are%20triggered%20by%20Lexi's%20play%2C%20which%20includes%20a%20homoerotic%20sequence%20mocking%20the%20male%20athletes%20at%20their%20school.%20He%20leaves%20to%20find%20his%20father%2C%20who%20moved%20out%20of%20their%20family%20home%2C%20and%20turns%20him%20in%20to%20the%20police%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20a%20USB%20drive%2C%20presumably%20containing%20evidence%20of%20Cal's%20wrongdoing.%20(It's%20unclear%20whether%20the%20USB%20includes%20the%20video%20of%20Cal's%20encounter%20with%20Jules%2C%20since%20Jules%20destroyed%20the%20only%20known%20copy.%20Nate%20told%20Jules%20he%20didn't%20make%20extra%20copies%2C%20though%20he%20could%20be%20lying.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHopefully%2C%20season%20three%20will%20reveal%20whether%20Cal%20was%20charged%20with%20any%20crimes%3B%20actor%20Eric%20Dane%20is%20listed%20among%20the%20series%20regulars.%20(Season%20three%20was%20filmed%20in%202025%2C%20before%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrity-deaths-famous-people-who-died-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDane%20died%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20suffering%20from%20ALS.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2279e44f95-6836-42e9-8383-8164891c356d%5C%22%3ENate%20also%20breaks%20up%20with%20Cassie%20in%20a%20fit%20of%20rage%2C%20but%20it's%20clear%20their%20relationship%20isn't%20over.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sydney%20Sweeney%20as%20Cassie%20and%20Jacob%20Elordi%20as%20Nate%20in%20the%20season%20two%20finale%20of%20%26quot%3BEuphoria.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cd74fae762ed6cfe4495ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESydney%20Sweeney%20as%20Cassie%20and%20Jacob%20Elordi%20as%20Nate%20in%20the%20season%20two%20finale%20of%20%26quot%3BEuphoria.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EEddy%20Chen%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Cassie%20and%20Maddy's%20fight%2C%20they%20quietly%20lick%20their%20wounds%20in%20the%20school%20bathroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20know%20what's%20funny%3F%26quot%3B%20Cassie%20says.%20%26quot%3BNate%20broke%20up%20with%20me%20before%20I%20even%20went%20on%20that%20stage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20worry%2C%26quot%3B%20Maddy%20replies%2C%20a%20mix%20of%20smugness%20and%20pity%20on%20her%20face.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20just%20the%20beginning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaddy%20had%20spent%20years%20stuck%20in%20her%20own%20toxic%20cycle%20with%20Nate%2C%20breaking%20up%20and%20reconciling%20despite%20his%20violent%20outbursts.%20She%20knows%20better%20than%20anyone%20what%20Cassie%20is%20signing%20up%20for%20%E2%80%94%20and%20judging%20by%20the%20season%20three%20trailers%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20Maddy%20was%20right.%20Just%20a%20few%20years%20after%20they%20graduated%20from%20high%20school%2C%20Nate%20and%20Cassie%20are%20engaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2250921101-2959-4a38-a549-bdc71f001fdd%5C%22%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Rue%20and%20Jules%20part%20ways.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rue%20kissing%20Jules'%20forehead%20on%20the%20season%20two%20finale%20of%20%26quot%3BEuphoria.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F621d0507bea1240018a8f4ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZendaya%20and%20Hunter%20Schafer%20on%20the%20season%20two%20finale%20of%20%26quot%3BEuphoria.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EEddy%20Chen%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERue%20and%20Jules%20click%20immediately%20upon%20meeting%20in%20season%20one.%20In%20the%20season%20two%20premiere%2C%20Rue%20finally%20confesses%20to%20Jules%20that%20she%20wants%20to%20be%20in%20a%20committed%20relationship.%20They%20kiss%2C%20but%20the%20tender%20moment%20is%20tinged%20with%20tragedy%3B%20Rue%20is%20deep%20into%20her%20relapse%2C%20and%20Jules%20has%20no%20idea%20how%20serious%20her%20drug%20use%20has%20become.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERue%20is%20also%20dealing%20with%20residual%20anger%20and%20resentment%20toward%20Jules%2C%20who%20ran%20away%20from%20home%20in%20the%20season%20one%20finale%2C%20leaving%20Rue%20behind.%20(At%20the%20time%2C%20Jules%20was%20being%20blackmailed%20by%20Nate%20and%20dealing%20with%20her%20mom's%20addiction%20issues%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20feeling%20wholly%20responsible%20for%20Rue's%20sobriety%2C%20so%20she%20freaked%20out.)%20All%20these%20simmering%2C%20unspoken%20emotions%20make%20navigating%20their%20relationship%20difficult.%20Rue%20retreats%20deeper%20into%20her%20addiction%2C%20while%20Jules%20seeks%20validation%20and%20affection%20from%20Elliot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Jules%20discovers%20that%20Rue%20is%20still%20doing%20drugs%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20only%20opiates%20anymore%2C%20but%20heroin%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffentanyl-addiction-toolkit-from-test-strips-to-addiction-hotlines-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efentanyl%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20too%20%E2%80%94%20she%20goes%20to%20Rue's%20mom%20for%20help.%20They%20decide%20to%20flush%20all%20of%20the%20drugs%20they%20find%20in%20Rue's%20room%20(the%20ones%20she%20got%20from%20Laurie)%20down%20the%20toilet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20season%20two%2C%20episode%20five%2C%20%26quot%3BStand%20Still%20Like%20the%20Hummingbird%2C%26quot%3B%20Rue's%20loved%20ones%20stage%20an%20intervention.%20Rue%20has%20a%20breakdown%20and%20cruelly%20tells%20Jules%20that%20their%20relationship%20is%20over.%20Actually%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20fucking%20dead%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20barely%20interact%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20season%2C%20even%20after%20Rue%20gets%20clean%2C%20except%20for%20a%20brief%20scene%20in%20the%20finale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20watching%20Lexi's%20play%2C%20Jules%20tells%20Rue%20that%20she%20loves%20and%20misses%20her.%20But%20Rue%20isn't%20ready%20to%20confront%20all%20the%20hurt%20they've%20caused%20each%20other.%20Instead%20of%20saying%20anything%20back%2C%20she%20kisses%20Jules%20on%20the%20head%20and%20walks%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJules%20was%20my%20first%20love%2C%26quot%3B%20Rue%20says%20in%20a%20voiceover.%20%26quot%3BI'd%20like%20to%20remember%20it%20that%20way.%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20that's%20actually%20true%2C%20though.%20I%20think%20I%20was%20high%20for%20too%20much%20of%20it.%20I%20know%20it%20wasn't%20easy%20for%20her%2C%20and%20I%20hope%20she%20forgives%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d4fd0f6b-d04e-4e36-9a53-8cf8c5efa088%5C%22%3EThe%20last%20time%20we%20see%20her%2C%20Rue%20is%20sober.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zendaya%20as%20Rue%20on%20the%20season%20two%20finale%20of%20%26quot%3BEuphoria.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F621cff5d101faf0019297313%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZendaya%20as%20Rue%20on%20the%20season%20two%20finale%20of%20%26quot%3BEuphoria.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EEddy%20Chen%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20final%20voiceover%20of%20season%20two%2C%20Rue%20reveals%20that%20she%20managed%20to%20stay%20clean%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20school%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wish%20I%20could%20say%20that%20was%20a%20decision%20I%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20Rue%20says.%20%26quot%3BIn%20some%20ways%2C%20it%20was%20just%20easier.%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20this%20feeling%20will%20last%20forever%2C%20but%20I%20am%20trying.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20we%20have%20plenty%20of%20evidence%20that%20Rue's%20sobriety%20is%20a%20tenuous%20thing%2C%20and%20trailers%20for%20season%20three%20seem%20to%20imply%20that%20another%20relapse%20is%20imminent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERue's%20mom%2C%20Leslie%20(Nika%20King)%2C%20even%20acknowledges%20that%20once%20Rue%20enters%20adulthood%2C%20there's%20little%20more%20she%20can%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20broke%20me.%20Completely%20broke%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20tells%20Rue%20in%20season%20two%2C%20episode%20seven%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Theater%20and%20Its%20Double.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20give%20up.%20You%20wanna%20kill%20yourself%20doing%20drugs%3F%20Go%20ahead%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continues.%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20convince%20you%20that%20your%20life%20is%20important.%20You're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20make%20that%20decision%20on%20your%20own.%20You'll%20be%2018%20soon%20and%20outta%20my%20house.%20And%20you're%20gonna%20make%20whatever%20decisions%20you're%20gonna%20make.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224a54f7a7-08c1-4406-89ca-4dae85afcfe1%5C%22%3EAshtray%20is%20killed%20when%20his%20and%20Fezco's%20house%20is%20raided%20by%20a%20SWAT%20team.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Javon%20Walton%20as%20Ashtray%20in%20%26quot%3BEuphoria%26quot%3B%20season%20two.%5C%22%2