0over%20breakfast.%20Sometimes%2C%20we'd%20arrange%20to%20meet%20up%20for%20certain%20activities.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20long%20as%20plans%20aligned%2C%20we'd%20come%20back%20together%20for%20lunch.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20though%2C%20we%20always%20sat%20together%20for%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20we%20booked%20Holland%20America's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fholland-america-have-it-all-package-worth-it-review-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHave%20It%20All%20package%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20even%20got%20a%20complimentary%20dinner%20at%20one%20of%20the%20premium%20restaurants.%20We%20all%20got%20dressed%20up%20(it%20was%20Independence%20Day%2C%20so%20some%20of%20the%20family%20embraced%20the%20red%2C%20white%2C%20and%20blue)%2C%20and%20sat%20together%20for%20a%20big%20group%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20extra%20special%2C%20as%20in%20years%20past%2C%20most%20of%20us%20would%20meet%20at%20my%20mother-in-law's%20for%20a%20Fourth%20of%20July%20cookout.%20Coming%20together%20for%20a%20formal%20dinner%20felt%20like%20we%20were%20honoring%20our%20tradition%20in%20a%20new%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22821b7cdf-e8cb-45bb-9a11-db1700ea6dd8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlus%2C%20we%20had%20lots%20of%20fun%20playing%20cards%20and%20doing%20trivia%20together%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22three%20people%20overlooking%20views%20from%20Alaskan%20cruise%20ship%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d572e8cc468aeec524cb70%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUncle%20Jack%2C%20Aunt%20Alice%2C%20and%20Mom%20Sharon%3Cp%3ETimothy%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20on-board%20activities%20we%20all%20seemed%20to%20enjoy%20was%20trivia.%20Each%20afternoon%2C%20we'd%20come%20together%20for%20music%20trivia%2C%20themed%20to%20a%20different%20decade%20each%20time.%20It%20was%20