ccording-frequent-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDenali%20National%20Park%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20we%20hiked%2C%20visited%20sled%20dogs%2C%20and%20white-water%20rafted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20much%20needed%20after%20a%20week%20on%20a%20cruise%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20I%20absolutely%20loved%20getting%20to%20spend%20so%20much%20time%20with%20my%20in-laws%2C%20Trent%20and%20I%20also%20enjoyed%20the%20moments%20with%20just%20the%20two%20of%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20a%20cruise%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20do%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgroup-inclusive-villa-worth-it-mexico-four-seasons-tamarindo-review-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emultigenerational%20family%20vacation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There's%20something%20for%20everyone%2C%20including%20several%20ways%20for%20families%20to%20spend%20time%20together%20and%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falaska-cruise-with-extended-family-planning-pros-cons-multigenerational-vacation-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775916721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d572e81a512d0a63e73557%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falaska-cruise-with-extended-family-planning-pros-cons-multigenerational-vacation-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Going%20on%20a%20cruise%20with%20extended%20family%20and%20in-laws%20isn't%20ideal%20for%20everyone%2C%20but%20our%20multigenerational%20group%20had%20a%20fun%20vacation%20with%20careful%20planning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Timothy%20Moore)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falaska-cruise-with-extended-family-planning-pros-cons-multigenerational-vacation-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How