-ate-adobe-graphic-designers-generative-ai-saas-software-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAdobe%3C%2Fa%3E%20Lightroom%2C%20he%20had%2050%20images%20that%20needed%20denoising%2C%20a%20tedious%20task%20typically%20done%20one-by-one.%20Instead%20of%20doing%20it%20manually%2C%20or%20even%20knowing%20how%20to%20batch%20it%2C%20Gostev%20let%20OpenAI's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenais-codex-lead-shares-tips-engineers-stand-out-email-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECodex%3C%2Fa%3E%20AI%20coding%20service%20figure%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20go%20and%20click%20into%20each%20one%20to%20denoise%2050%20photos.%20That%20sounds%20like%20hard%20work%2C%20so%20I%20just%20got%20Codex%20to%20go%20and%20work%20out%20how%20to%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Gostev%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BIt%20just%20worked.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20notable%20is%20how%20Codex%20pulled%20this%20off%3A%20not%20through%20an%20official%20API%2C%20plugin%2C%20or%20browser%20workaround%2C%20but%20by%20somehow%20interfacing%20directly%20with%20the%20desktop%20app%2C%20despite%20no%20clear%20support%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGostev%20is%20technically%20advanced%20and%20what%20he%20did%20here%20is%20something%20I%20probably%20couldn't%20do.%20Still%2C%20it's%20a%20glimpse%20of%20where%20AI%20agents%20are%20heading%3A%20not%20just%20assisting%2C%20but%20autonomously%20navigating%20and%20operating%20software%20like%20a%20human%20would%20(or%20in%20this%20case%20doing%20it%20faster%20and%20better%20than%20a%20smart%20human).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Reach%20out%20to%20me%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabarr%40busin