tion%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAugusta's%20caddies%20at%20the%20time%20didn't%20use%20yardage%20books%2C%20instead%20relying%20on%20course%20knowledge%20and%20feel%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.golfheritage.org%2Fblog%2F5-little-known-masters-and-augusta-national-facts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGolf%20Heritage%20Society.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPlayers%20are%20now%20allowed%20to%20use%20their%20own%20caddies%2C%20but%20they%20must%20wear%20the%20Augusta%20uniform%3A%20a%20green%20hat%20and%20a%20white%20jumpsuit.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tiger%20Woods%20and%20Justin%20Thomas%20walk%20the%20course%20at%20Augusta%20National%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F624c77c1bb219a00181bc774%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221529%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETiger%20Woods%20and%20Justin%20Thomas%20walk%20the%20course%20at%20Augusta%20National.%3Cp%3EAugusta%20National%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.masters.com%2Fen_US%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2022-04-08%2Fmasters_101_the_caddie_jumpsuit.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMasters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20the%20late%201940s%2C%20caddies%20began%20to%20wear%20these%20outfits%20so%20they%20could%20be%20set%20apart%20from%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20year%2C%20caddies%20at%20Augusta%20can%20wear%20whatever%20they%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPatrons%20aren't%20allowed%20to%20wear%20their%20hats%20backward.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22964%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22augusta%20masters%20hats%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d90c2705c9b303c4e76f33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22723%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEven%20a%20top-ranked%20player%2C%20Rickie%20Fowler%2C%20was%20advised%20to%20obey%20the%20rule.%3Cp%3EScott%20Halleran%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rule%20even%20applies%20to%20players.%20In%202011%2C%20top-ranked%20Rickie%20Fowler%20was%20wearing%20his%20hat%20backwards%20at%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20where%20he%20was%20promptly%20ordered%20to%20turn%20it%20around%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.yahoo.com%2Fblogs%2Fgolf-devil-ball-golf%2Frickie-fowler-gets-lesson-augusta-national-decorum-210241267.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYahoo%20Sports%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPatrons%20can%20bring%20collapsible%20chairs%20to%20sit%20on%2C%20but%20they%20must%20not%20have%20armrests.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222223%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Masters%20golf%20chairs%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d90c5396ef6a4c9d121a04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChairs%20at%20Augusta%20National%20for%20the%20Masters.%3Cp%3EEzra%20Shaw%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Golfweek%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPatrons%20can%20also%20arrive%20early%2C%20stake%20a%20claim%20to%20a%20small%20plot%20of%20land%20on%20the%20course%2C%20place%20their%20chair%2C%20and%20then%20wander%20around%20the%20course%20without%20losing%20their%20spot.%20Most%20own%20the%20official%20green%20Masters%20chair%2C%20which%20sells%20for%20%2430%20in%20the%20shop%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgolf.com%2Fnews%2Funraveling-masters-greatest-unwritten-traditions-chairs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGolf.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20an%20unwritten%20rule%20that%20it%20is%20acceptable%20to%20sit%20in%20an%20unoccupied%20chair%20as%20long%20as%20you%20are%20willing%20to%20move%20when%20the%20owner%20returns.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERunning%20is%20not%20allowed%20unless%20you%20are%20a%20player.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222223%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hideki%20Matsuyama%20runs%20past%20the%20aza