-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eheadlines%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20he%20made%20a%20quick%20run%20to%20a%20bunker%20to%20get%20some%20sand%20to%20take%20home.%20He%20was%20quickly%20arrested%20and%20thrown%20in%20jail.%20The%20charges%20were%20ultimately%20dropped%2C%20but%20he%20says%20the%20incident%20cost%20him%20%2420%2C000%20and%20led%20to%20depression%20because%20of%20how%20he%20was%20treated.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMeanwhile%2C%20those%20bunkers%20at%20Augusta%20are%20filled%20with%20mining%20waste.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222223%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Augusta%20National%20bunker%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d9238896ef6a4c9d121abc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESand%20in%20Augusta%20National%20bunkers%20are%20a%20byproduct%20of%20mining.%3Cp%3EAl%20Tielemans%20%2FSports%20Illustrated%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sand%20comes%20from%20Spruce%20Pine%20mining%20area%20near%20the%20Blue%20Ridge%20Mountains%20in%20North%20Carolina%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthegolfnewsnet.com%2Fryan_ballengee%2F2026%2F04%2F09%2Fwhy-augusta-national-bunkers-white-sand-where-it-comes-from-112934%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGolf%20News%20Net%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20sand%20is%20merely%20a%20byproduct%20from%20the%20quartz%20and%20feldspar%20mining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EYou%20can%20only%20ask%20for%20autographs%20in%20one%20part%20of%20the%20course.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222219%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jordan%20Spieth%20at%20the%20Masters%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d9243e96ef6a4c9d121ac0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221664%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJordan%20Spieth%20signed%20an%20autograph%20at%20the%20Masters.%3Cp%3EJIM%20WATSON%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tournament%20enforces%20the%20rule%