quirks-traditions-at-augusta%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22No%20birds%2C%20cheap%20food%2C%20and%20artificial%20dye%20in%20the%20water%20are%20just%20a%20few%20of%20the%20Masters'%20quirks.%20See%20everything%20that%20makes%20the%20tournament%20unique.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cgaines%40insider.com%20(Cork%20Gaines%2CJames%20LaForge)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-masters-biggest-quirks-traditions-at-augusta%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20ran%20a%20successful%20brick-and-mortar%20business%20for%20decades.%20I%20shut%20it%20down%20in%20my%2050s%20to%20reinvent%20myself%20and%20my%20career.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Susan%20Teresa%20posing%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d562251a512d0a63e734b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20ran%20a%20photography%20studio.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Susan%20Teresa%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20ran%20a%20successful%20brick-and-mortar%20store%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20decided%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20business%20in%20my%2050s%2C%20turning%20my%20back%20on%20an%20identity%20I%20had%20built.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20reconnecting%20with%20what%20lights%20me%20up%20and%20reinventing%20myself%20at%2056.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20I%20woke%20up%20to%20a%20difficult%20truth%3A%20I%20was%20unhappy.%20A%20solopreneur%20since%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20I'd%20built%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscale-back-six-figure-business-income-family-time-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esix-figure%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20raising%20three%20boys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20workaholic%20drive%20meant%20giving%20my%20all%20to%20every%20client.%20It%20paid%20off%3A%20the%20photography%20studio%20I%20ran%20earned%20flawless%20five-star%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fgoogle-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20reviews%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20long%20roster%20of%20loyal%20clients.%20I%20even%20earned%20industry%20recognition%20(including%20a%20book%20deal%20and%20invitations%20to%20speak%20on%20stages%20at%20national%20events).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20around%20me%2C%20things%20had%20been%20changing.%20The%20market%20had%20grown%20more%20crowded%20every%20year.%20The%20unique%20approach%20I'd%20brought%20to%20the%20marketplace%20had%20become%20common%20practice.%20And%20I%20%E2%80%94%20at%2055%20%E2%80%94%20was%20not%20the%20same%20person%20as%20the%2030-something%20who'd%20started%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20slowly%20found%20myself%20quietly%20wondering%20whether%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-fix-mistakes-business-owner-entrepreneur-according-to-coach-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20to%20unravel%20a%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20had%20taken%2020%20years%20to%20build.%20Friends%20and%20family%20wondered%20if%20walking%20away%20made%20any%20sense.%20But%20deep%20inside%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20yearning%20for%20change.%20I'd%20lost%20touch%20with%20the%20parts%20of%20myself%20that%20once%20felt%20creative%20and%20inspired.%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20grow%20and%20evolve.%20The%20life%20I'd%20built%20no%20longer%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2271047757-44bf-4815-b8d8-3e7a0c25edf2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELeaping%20into%20the%20unknown%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%20of%202024%2C%20I%20closed%20the%20business%20for%20good.%20It%20wasn't%20easy.%20It%20meant%20stepping%20away%20from%20an%20identity%20I'd%20carefully%20built%2C%20and%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoney-saving-habits-feel-more-financially-secure-advice-sun-life-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20security%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20provided.%20I%20needed%20space%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20I%20wanted%20next%20as%20I%20entered%20the%20second%20half%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20locked%20the%20doors%20for%20the%20last%20time%2C%20I%20felt%20happy.%20Relief%20washed%20away%20any%20regret%20I%20thought%20I'd%20have.%20I%20felt%20lighter%20%E2%80%94%20free%20from%20the%20burden%20of%20a%20business%20I%20no%20longer%20enjoyed%2C%20and%20that%20no%20longer%20fueled%20my%20own%20growth.%20I'd%20been%20stagnant%2C%20and%20now%20I%20was%20free%20to%20move%20forward%2C%20to%20find%20new%20ways%20to%20express%20myself%2C%20to%20do%20work%20that%20felt%20meaningful%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20connected%20with%20lots%20of%20other%20women%20my%20age%2C%20I've%20learned%20I'm%20not%20alone%20in%20making%20a%20midlife%20leap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fda01f14-27a2-4139-bc84-81d1f3bf6038%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERediscovering%20purpose%20in%20midlife%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20giving%20myself%20space%20and%20settling%20into%20a%20slower%20pace%20with%20no%20more%2048-hour%20workweeks%2C%20I%20dove%20into%20learning.%20I%20signed%20up%20for%20a%20few%20courses%2C%20curious%20to%20see%20where%20inspiration%20would%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20reflected%20on%20all%20the%20iterations%20I'd%20experienced%20in%20the%20past%3A%20corporate%20professional%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-navigate-toughest-job-market-apply-for-jobs-last-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecareer%20coach%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20trainer%2C%20and%20small-business%20owner.%20I%20then%20crafted%20a%20list%20of%20my%20skills%2C%20knowledge%20areas%2C%20and%20natural%20abilities.%20Then%20I%20repeated%20the%20process%20from%20the%20inside%20out%2C%20reflecting%20on%20where%20I%20felt%20excitement%20and%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuddenly%2C%20I%20saw%20all%20the%20unwritten%20books%20I'd%20placed%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bsomeday%26quot%3B%20she