ges%2C%20get%20a%20master's%20degree%2C%20and%20be%20globally%20aware.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20studied%20journalism%20and%20media%2C%20and%20I%20leaned%20into%20storytelling%20early%20on.%20I%20spent%20time%20abroad%20multiple%20times%20in%20Rome%2C%20Florence%2C%20Kuwait%2C%20and%20Scotland.%20I%20learned%20how%20to%20navigate%20new%20cultures%2C%20new%20systems%2C%20and%20new%20expectations.%20I%20became%20fluent%20in%20spaces%20that%20were%20not%20designed%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-gen-ivy-league-student-couldnt-connect-rich-classmates-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst-generation%20student%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduating%2C%20I%20went%20on%20to%20earn%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmasters-degree-scam-higher-education-millennials-genz-student-loan-debt-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaster's%20degree%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20international%20affairs%20as%20part%20of%20the%20inaugural%20cohort%20at%20John%20Cabot%20University%20in%20Rome%20(again).%20I%20focused%20on%20global%20justice%2C%20human%20rights%2C%20and%20representation.%20I%20contributed%20to%20research%20on%20the%20gig%20economy%2C%20attended%20UN%20conferences%20both%20in%20Italy%20and%20Azerbaijan%2C%20and%20built%20what%20I%20thought%20was%20a%20strong%2C%20competitive%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20completed%20my%20MA%20degree%20early%2C%20believing%20I%20had%20done%20everything%20right.%20But%20I%20still%20can't%20find%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2274521666-cbfc-4986-a28c-a5b3e9c543a6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20applied%20everywhere%2C%20across%20countries%20and%20industries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20graduating%2C%20I've%20applied%20to%20over%201%2C000%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20includes%20roles%20in%20Rome%20with%20UN%20agencies%2C%20NGOs%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmercy-corps-generative-ai-