5C%22614%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nicolette%20Alexandra%20Brito-Cruz%20dressed%20in%20her%20graduation%20gown%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d6871bcc468aeec524cf9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22461%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20earned%20her%20master's%20degree.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Nicolette%20Alexandra%20Brito-Cruz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20do%20you%20do%20when%20there's%20no%20outcome%20at%20all%3F%20When%20positions%20stay%20open%20indefinitely.%20When%20companies%20repost%20roles%20without%20hiring.%20When%20you%20make%20it%20through%20multiple%20steps%20and%20still%20hear%20nothing%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20creates%20this%20constant%20loop%20in%20your%20mind.%20You%20start%20questioning%20everything%3A%20your%20degree%2C%20your%20experience%2C%20and%20the%20choices%20you%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20everything%20I%20was%20told%20would%20make%20me%20employable.%20Yet%2C%20I've%20never%20felt%20more%20unsure%20about%20where%20I%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2279b46f5b-407e-4849-83e0-b2a331d38625%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFreelancing%20became%20my%20way%20of%20earning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20some%20point%2C%20I%20had%20to%20shift%20my%20focus%20from%20waiting%20to%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20undergrad%2C%20I%20spent%20four%20years%20working%20in%20publicity%20and%20creative%20marketing.%20That%20became%20the%20one%20thing%20I%20could%20return%20to%20when%20the%20job%20market%20kept%20shutting%20me%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I%20freelance%20as%20a%20creative%20director%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarketing-pro-quit-job-travel-and-rethink-her-career-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarketing%20professional%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20design%20campaigns%2C%20create%20visual%20content%2C%20and%20work%20with%20clients%20to%20build%20cohesive%20brand%20identities.%20I've%20worked%20on%20everything%20from%20social%20media%20strategy%20to%20email%20marketing%20to%20photoshoots%20to%20editorial%20visuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20stable%20or%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsneaky-truth-ai-layoffs-switcheroo-meta-microsoft-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efull-time%20role%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20desire%20for%20myself.%20But%20it's%20something%20I%20built%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFreelancing%20has%20taught%20me%20how%20to%20trust%20my%20skills%20in%20a%20different%20way.%20It's%20shown%20me%20that%20I%20don't%20need%20permission%20to%20create%20meaningful%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20there's%20a%20difference%20between%20surviving%20and%20feeling%20secure.%20I'm%20still%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20bridge%20that%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2270d3de52-fec5-435a-a7ef-496593ccb328%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20having%20stability%20forced%20me%20to%20rethink%20what%20I%20actually%20want%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20long%20time%2C%20I%20was%20chasing%20stability%20as%20it%20was%20defined%20for%20me%3A%20a%20full%20time%20job%2C%20steady%20paycheck%2C%20and%20clear%20title.%20But%20not%20having%20that%20has%20pushed%20me%20to%20ask%20a%20different%20question.%20What%20kind%20of%20work%20do%20I%20actually%20want%20to%20be%20doing%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20keeps%20bringing%20me%20back%20to%20storytelling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20want%20to%20be%20a%20creative%20director%20who%20focuses%20on%20telling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthis-trio-wants-to-help-bipoc-in-the-consumer-industry-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBIPOC%20stories%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20care%20and%20accuracy.%20I%20want%20to%20create%20media%20that%20doesn't%20flatten%20people%20into%20stereotypes%20or%20reduce%20cultures%20into%20trends.%20I%20want%20to%20build%20projects%20that%20feel%20honest%2C%20layered%2C%20and%20intentional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20work%20I've%20been%20drawn%20to%20for%20years.%20It's%20also%20the%20work%20I%20kept%20putting%20off%20because%20I%20thought%20I%20needed%20something%20more%20%26quot%3Bstable%26quot%3B%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I'm%20starting%20to%20see%20that%20maybe%20the%20path%20I%20was%20following%20was%20never%20designed%20to%20lead%20me%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a8416016-5bea-4763-98ea-967804fb9d71%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20still%20figuring%20it%20out%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20have%20a%20clean%20ending%20to%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20still%20applying%20for%20jobs%20while%20freelancing%2C%20and%20trying%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20a%20system%20that%20feels%20unpredictable%20and%2C%20at%20times%2C%20impossible%20to%20navigate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20also%20know%20this%3A%20the%20effort%20I've%20put%20in%20hasn't%20been%20wasted.%20It%20just%20didn't%20lead%20me%20where%20I%20expected.%20Maybe%20that%20means%20I%20have%20to%20build%20something%20different%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funemployed-recent-college-grad-applied-thousand-jobs-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775905621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d686bfcc468aeec524cf9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funemployed-recent-college-grad-applied-thousand-jobs-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20studied%20abroad%20four%20times%2C%20I%20earned%20my%20master's%2C%20and%20I%20became%20a%20global%20scholar.%20But%20I%20still%20can't%20find%20a%20job.%20All%20my%20applications%20go%20unanswered.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Nicolette%20Alexandra%20Brito-Cruz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funemployed-recent-college-grad-applied-thousand-jobs-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22amp