g%20with%20workers%20who've%20found%20themselves%20at%20a%20corporate%20crossroads%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20due%20to%20a%20layoff%2C%20resignation%2C%20job%20search%2C%20or%20shifting%20workplace%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShare%20your%20story%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSechTVqVWQve8iqYssNriCXdtwwdgGRixNNZpmslSKBQqIJ8g%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dheader%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efilling%20out%20this%20form%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20contacting%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzinkula%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejzinkula%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20via%20Signal%20at%20jzinkula.29.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8699b1f-591f-4503-8b68-616e958d7f43%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EJoining%20the%20ranks%20of%20the%20overemployed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Michael%20stumbled%20upon%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foveremployed-workers-secret-two-multiple-jobs-salaries-tech-tips-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Boveremployed%26quot%3B%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Reddit%2C%20where%20users%20share%20stories%20and%20advice%20about%20working%20multiple%20jobs%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20he%20learned%2C%20the%20more%20attractive%20it%20seemed.%20His%20current%20recruiting%20job%20wasn't%20demanding%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-fast-is-economic-recovery-pandemic-december-jobs-report-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehiring%20was%20starting%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20boom%20across%20the%20US%20economy%20%E2%80%94%20which%20meant%20more%20demand%20for%20recruiters%20%E2%80%94%20and%20many%20roles%20were%20remote%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic%2C%20which%20made%20job%20juggling%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20didn't%20want%20to%20rush%20it.%20Michael%20had%20recently%20started%20a%20new%20full-time%20remote%20role%2C%20doing%20internal%20recruiting%20in%20the%20e-commerce%20industry.%20He%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20he%20felt%20settled%20before%20taking%20on%20a%20whole%20new%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20early%202022%2C%20he'd%20grown%20used%20to%20the%20workload.%20He%20also%20suspected%20that%20the%20window%20to%20capitalize%20on%20the%20overemployment%20trend%20was%20closing%2C%20in%20part%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-fed-taper-rate-hike-pulls-support-wolfenbarger-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edue%20to%20economic%20concerns%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20hiring%20might%20slow%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20okay%2C%20'It's%20time%20for%20job%20number%20two%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20June%2C%20Michael%20started%20a%20second%20technical%20recruiter%20position%2C%20in%20the%20finance%20industry.%20Like%20his%20original%20job%2C%20his%20new%20position%20wasn't%20very%20demanding.%20While%20the%20company%20was%20hiring%2C%20many%20open%20roles%20already%20had%20preferred%20candidates%2C%20leaving%20him%20with%20relatively%20little%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20said%20that%20on%20a%20typical%20day%2C%20he'd%20work%20his%20original%20job%20from%20roughly%206%20a.m.%20to%2010%20a.m.%2C%20take%20a%20break%2C%20then%20focus%20on%20his%20second%20job%20for%20about%20two%20hours%20%E2%80%94%20about%20six%20hours%20of%20work%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20that%20I%20was%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20even%20working%20a%20full%2040%20hours%20a%20week.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e0d40bd5-3964-461c-a76c-d5d6964f1100%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoing%20from%20two%20jobs%20to%20three%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20working%20two%20jobs%20felt%20comfortable%2C%20Michael%20decided%20to%20go%20for%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20September%202022%2C%20he'd%20landed%20a%20third%20technical%20recruiter%20position%20at%20a%20consulting%20firm.%20Michael%20soon%20found%20that%20his%20new%20role%20was%20the%20most%20demanding%2C%20so%20he%20restructured%20his%20workday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20began%20waking%20up%20at%205%20a.m.%20to%20work%20his%20original%20role%20for%20about%20four%20hours.%20After%20a%20break%2C%20he'd%20bounce%20between%20his%20other%20two%20jobs%20from%20roughly%2010%20a.m.%20to%201%20p.m.%20After%20lunch%2C%20he'd%20finish%20off%20any%20outstanding%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20juggling%20three%20full-time%20jobs%2C%20Michael%20said%20he%20still%20typically%20didn't%20work%2040%20hours%20a%20week.%20But%20by%20late%202022%2C%20the%20hiring%20boom%20that%20had%20made%20his%20overemployment%20possible%20began%20to%20fade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225ab58b73-60f1-41e4-b384-0f32c8529184%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20end%20of%20overemployment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fall%20of%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-bubble-recession-risk-investing-strategy-david-rosenberg-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecession%20fears%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20on%20the%20rise%2C%20and%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20had%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomic-outlook-inflation-response-mistake-federal-reserve-ben-bernanke-stagflation-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraising%20interest%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20combat%20inflation%20%E2%80%94%20leading%20some%20employers%20to%20scrap%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhiring-freeze-things-to-think-about-your-company-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edelay%20hiring%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHiring%20managers%20that%20I%20was%20working%20with%20were%20basically%20saying%2C%20'If%20we%20don't%20get%20these%20positions%20hired%20soon%2C%20the%20budget%20goes%20away%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20October%2C%20most%20of%20the%20positions%20Michael%20had%20been%20trying%20to%20fill%20were%20closed%20without%20a%20hire%20%E2%80%94%20something%20he%20said%20played%20out%20across%20all%20three%20of%20his%20jobs%20over%20a%20few-week%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20suspected%20that%20his%20diminishing%20workload%20could%20put%20his%20jobs%20at%20risk%2C%20and%20he%20was%20proven%20correct.%20Michael%20said%20that%20after%20being%20laid%20off%20from%20his%20original%20job%20in%20late%202022%2C%20he%20was%20laid%20off%20from%20his%20remaining%20roles%20over%20the%20following%20months%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flayoffs-sweeping-the-us-these-are-the-companies-making-cuts-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejob%20market%20cooled%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Over%20the%20next%20two%20years%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20find%20some%20new%20positions%20but%2C%20in%202024%2C%20he%20faced%20a%20stretch%20of%20several%20months%20without%20any%20work%20%E2%80%94%20which%20he%20attributed%20to%20a%20slowdown%20in%20hiring%20for%20recruiting%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20said%20his%20job%20search%20took%20a%20significant%20toll%20on%20his%20finances%20and%20forced%20him%20to%20temporarily%20rely%20on%20others%20for%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20couch%20surf%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20whole%20life%20changed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22979a20fb-3549-4f42-9682-242f962fe376%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoving%20on%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20Michael%20began%20to%20question%20whether%20he%20could%20still%20make%20a%20living%20in%20recruiting.%20It%20was%20difficult%20to%20find%20and%20retain%20work%2C%20and%20available%20roles%20paid%20significantly%20less%20than%20he'd%20come%20to%20expect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20Michael%20pivoted%20to%20the%20insurance%20sector%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhich%20he%20thought%20offered%20him%20a%20better%20chance%20at%20a%20stable%2C%20sustainable%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20Michael%20said%20he%20wishes%20he%20never%20had%20to%20pursue%20overemployment%20in%20the%20first%20place%20%E2%80%94%20that%20one%20job%20would%20have%20been%20enough%20to%20reach%20his%20financial%20goals.%20But%20he%20said%20he%20doesn't%20regret%20job%20juggling%2C%20even%20if%20it%20didn't%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20great%20until%20it%20wasn't%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foveremployed-millennial-recruiter-secretly-worked-remote-job-market-layoffs-california-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775901721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d9451d96ef6a4c9d121c0a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foveremployed-millennial-recruiter-secretly-worked-remote-job-market-layoffs-california-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20recruiter%20made%20%24280K%20secretly%20working%203%20remote%20jobs.%20Then%20a%20hiring%20slowdown%20forced%20him%20to%20change%20careers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jzinkula%40insider.com%20(Jacob%20Zinkula)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foveremployed-millennial-recruiter-secretly-worked-remote-job-market-layoffs-california-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22EC%20transfers%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Home%20Secretary%2C%20appoints%20K%20Manivasan%20immediately%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775901642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-05%2F24%2Ffull%2F1716528880-3511.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Felections%2Ftamil-nadu-elections%2Fec-transfers-tamil-nad