n%20attorney%2C%20her%20packed%20schedule%20as%20a%20mom%20of%20two%2C%20and%20the%20hustle%20of%20New%20York%20City%20living%20are%20eclipsed%20by%20the%20more%20than%20100%20pounds%20of%20metal%20she's%20about%20to%20lift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20easy%20%E2%80%94%20everything%20in%20her%20mind%20and%20body%20is%20alert%20to%20the%20challenge%2C%20the%20possibility%20of%20failure.%20She%20hoists%20the%20weight%20onto%20her%20shoulders%2C%20the%20ends%20of%20the%20barbell%20dipping%20under%20massive%20plates%2C%20and%20she%20squats%2C%20driving%20through%20her%20legs%20and%20core%20to%20propel%20the%20equivalent%20of%20a%20young%20hippopotamus%20down%20and%20back%20up%2C%20repeatedly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227129%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Deb%20Stern%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d7e963f976785dcb18fe89%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225092%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAttorney%20Deb%20Stern%20loves%20heavy%20barbell%20back%20squats%2C%20and%20said%20weightlifting%20keeps%20her%20calm%20and%20centered%20even%20with%20a%20busy%20caseload.%3Cp%3ESydney%20Krantz%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20her%20workouts%2C%20Stern%20said%2C%20everything%20else%20in%20her%20life%20feels%20easier.%20She's%20done%20the%20hard%20thing%2C%20trained%20herself%20to%20face%20down%20uncertainty%20and%20discomfort%2C%20and%20came%20out%20stronger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%20gym%2C%20Stern%20is%20a%20structured%20finance%20lawyer%2C%20a%20specialist%20in%20navigating%20the%20complex%20legal%20framework%20behind%20massive%20piles%20of%20cash%20in%20loans%20and%20investments.%20It's%20a%20high-stakes%20environment%20that%20demands%20performance%20every%20time%20Stern%20calls%20a%20client%20or%20leads%20a%20team%20on%20a%20new%20project.%20And%20after%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-your-workout-is-working-from-personal-trainer-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egood%20gym%20session%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she's%20not%20only%20up%20to%20the%20challenge%2C%20but%20embraces%20it%20head-on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20happens%20at%20work%20every%20day.%20Before%20weight%20training%2C%20I%20would%20have%20been%20super%20stressed%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Stern%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20gets%20thrown%20at%20me%2C%20I%20can%20handle%20it.%20Bring%20it%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Deb%20Stern%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d7ed9bf976785dcb18feb6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBuilding%20strength%20in%20the%20gym%20translates%20into%20better%20resilience%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20handle%20real-world%20stresses%2C%20such%20as%20leadership%20roles%20at%20work.%3Cp%3ESydney%20Krantz%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20the%20endorphins%20of%20exercise%20(though%20that%20helps).%20In%20an%20era%20defined%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-to-take-foundayo-new-weight-loss-pill-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGLP-1%20drugs%3C%2Fa%3E%20promising%20to%20shed%20pounds%2C%20many%20women%20in%20business%20and%20tech%20are%20increasingly%20turning%20toward%20gains%20instead%20to%20project%20an%20image%20of%20competence%2C%20drive%2C%20and%20self-mastery.%20For%20these%20women%2C%20lifting%20weights%20is%20a%20way%20to%20signal%20ambition%20and%20confidence%2C%20and%20to%20showcase%20their%20discipline.%20And%20women%20aren't%20lifting%20alone%20%E2%80%94%20gyms%20have%20turned%20workouts%20into%20a%20social%20ritual%2C%20moving%20networking%20from%20happy%20hour%20to%20the%20gym%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20strong%20is%20the%20new%20skinny%2C%20and%20that's%20why%20we%20keep%20seeing%20it%20with%20young%20women%20changing%20their%20body%20image%20through%20strength%20training%2C%26quot%3B%20Jim%20Rowley%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrunch-ceo-stays-fit-busy-schedule-protein-shakes-pilates-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECEO%20of%20Crunch%20Fitness%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20interest%20climbing%2C%20gyms%20and%20studios%20are%20downsizing%20their%20cardio%20equipment%20to%20make%20way%20for%20the%20weights.%20For%20instance%2C%20Gold's%20Gym%20has%20decreased%20its%20cardio%20space%20by%20about%2015%25%2C%20according%20to%20the%20director%20of%20performance%20Erin%20Gregory.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20they've%20added%2030%25%20more%20strength%20training%20equipment%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgyms-outdated-cardio-no-squat-racks-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20squat%20racks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20benches%2C%20and%20free%20weights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWomen%20are%20getting%20more%20confidence%20on%20the%20weight%20room%20floor%2C%20which%20I%20love%20to%20see%2C%26quot%3B%20Gregory%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20sculpted%20biceps%20or%20heavy%20squats%2C%20strength%20training%20is%20also%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20antiaging%20movement%20that%20finally%20acknowledges%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuild-more-muscle-less-time-pro-tips-top-exercise-scientist-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehealthy%20muscle%20mass%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20key%20factor%20in%20living%20a%20longer%2C%20healthier%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227066%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Deb%20Stern%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d7ec0a05c9b303c4e76a9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225047%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKettlebells%2C%20barbells%2C%20dumbbells%2C%20and%20exercise%20machines%20are%20among%20the%20options%20for%20women%20looking%20to%20get%20strong.%3Cp%3ESydney%20Krantz%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20ambitious%20women%20in%20the%20workplace%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20pumping%20iron%20helps%20build%20the%20mental%20strength%20needed%20to%20climb%20an%20ever-steeper%20corporate%20ladder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224420eafc-722e-40ac-96e0-6753a5515a4b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20right%20to%20bare%20arms%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20era%20where%20longevity%20is%20the%20ultimate%20status%20symbol%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20beat%20strength%20training.%20Showing%20off%20a%20sculpted%2C%20muscular%20physique%20signals%20resilience%20for%20the%20long%20haul.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20growing%20body%20of%20research%20suggests%20that%20working%20out%2C%20particularly%20with%20resistance%20training%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-longevity-scientist-shared-his-weekly-workout-routine-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeffective%20anti-aging%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20we%20have.%20Women%20are%20increasingly%20the%20focus%20of%20that%20research%20after%20decades%20of%20being%20assumed%20to%20be%20smaller%2C%20less%20muscular%20versions%20of%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20they%20actually%20started%20to%20study%20the%20impacts%20of%20strength%20training%20on%20women%2C%20the%20evidence%20supporting%20women's%20strength%20training%20was%20just%20unbelievable%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20personal%20trainer%20Kristie%20Larson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20tabindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20data-media-container%3D%5C%22image%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22img%5C%22%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-figure-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Deb%20Stern%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d7ec61f976785dcb18fea6%3Fwidth%3D1300%26format%3Djpeg%26auto%3Dwebp%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%5Cn%3Cfigcaption%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-caption%5C%22%3E%5CnWeight%20lifting%20has%20a%20myriad%20of%20benefits%20for%20women%2C%20from%20stronger%20bones%20to%20increased%20energy%20and%20improved%20mood.%20%3Cspan%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-source%5C%22%3E%5CnSydney%20Krantz%20for%20BI%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20women%20are%20understanding%2C%20if%20I%20want%20to%20be%20independent%20into%20old%20age%2C%20then%20it's%20really%20important%20for%20me%20to%20start%20thinking%20about%20my%20bone%20health%20and%20building%20muscle%20mass%20instead%20of%20the%20narrative%20that%20we%20were%20constantly%20exposed%20to%20of%20just%20working%20out%20to%20be%20skinny.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWomen's%20prestige%20was%20once%20tied%20to%20staying%20small%2C%20maintaining%20a%20petite%20figure%20and%20tiny%20waist%20as%20evidence%20that%20we%20could%20have%20it%20all%3A%20a%20career%2C%2090%20minutes%20or%20more%20of%20cardio%20a%20day%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20subsist%20on%20salads%20and%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reporter%20Anne%20Marie%20Chaker%20said%20she%20vividly%20recalls%2C%20as%20a%20rookie%20journalist%2C%20stepping%20into%20the%20office%20elevator%20with%20an%20editor%20who%20tried%20to%20compliment%20her%20by%20asking%20if%20she%20had%20lost%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnter%20Ozempic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anne%20Marie%20Chaker%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d7ea3796ef6a4c9d12156b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnne%20Marie%20Chaker%20started%20strength%20training%20in%202017.%20She%20details%20the%20benefits%20in%20her%20book%20%26quot%3BLift%3A%20How%20Women%20Can%20Reclaim%20Their%20Physical%20Power%20and%20Transform%20Their%20Lives.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EStella%20Kalinina%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-glp-1-drugs-ozempic-wegovy-mounjaro-effects-future-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprescription%20weight%20loss%20medications%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20taken%20the%20world%20by%20storm%2C%20with%20about%201%20in%20every%208%20American%20adults%20trying%20them.%20While%20GLP-1s%20are%20by%20no%20means%20a%20shortcut%20to%20weight%20loss%20or%20health%2C%20the%20drugs%20have%20offered%20an%20unprecedented%20means%20to%20change%20one's%20body%20far%20beyond%20what%20diet%20or%20supplements%20can%20consistently%20do%20alone.%20As%20the%20drugs%20have%20become%20more%20affordable%2C%20they're%20also%20reshaping%20access%20to%20long-term%20weight%20loss%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20you%20can't%20buy%20muscle%20%E2%80%94%20yet.%20It%20takes%20hours%20of%20sweat%20and%20months%20of%20consistency%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkim-kardashian-trainer-5-minute-workout-build-muscle-burn-fat-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuild%20an%20athletic%20body%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20showing%20off%20a%20muscular%20physique%20has%20become%20a%20status%20symbol%20boasting%20discipline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fd99ffa8-00f3-449c-9d4d-b353944a0dc9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETraining%20became%20a%20corporate%20cheat%20code%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20ever%2C%20women%20are%20leveraging%20their%20physical%20strength%20to%20signal%20not%20only%20their%20dedication%2C%20but%20their%20capacity%20for%20leadership%2C%20said%20Pattie%20Sellers%2C%20a%20former%20assistant%20managing%20editor%20at%20Fortune.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20two%20decades%2C%20Sellers%20chaired%20the%20magazine's%20running%20list%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20powerful%20women%2C%20who%20often%20showed%20up%20in%20historically%20male-dominated%20fields%20like%20business%20and%20tech.%20In%20a%20bygone%20era%2C%20men%20in%20charge%20would%20broker%20deals%20over%20scotch%20and%20cigars%2C%20or%20lavish%20dinners%20on%20the%20company's%20dime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anne%20Marie%20Chaker%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d7ed36f976785dcb18feb2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESculpted%20arms%20have%20become%20a%20status%20symbol%20for%20women.%3Cp%3EStella%20Kalinina%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20won't%20cut%20it%20in%20today's%20high-stress%20environment%2C%20where%20the%20job%20requires%20real%20stamina%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20mental%20and%20physical%20resilience%20that%20can't%20be%20faked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%20optics%2C%26quot%3B%20Sellers%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20simply%20not%20going%20to%20last%20if%20you%20are%20not%20strong%20physically%2C%20mentally%2C%20emotionally.%20It%20is%20too%20much%20of%20a%20pressure%20cooker%20world%20for%20leaders%20to%20survive%2C%20no%20matter%20your%20industry%2C%20unless%20you're%20focusing%20on%20health%20and%20wellness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20women%20like%20Sarah%20Robb-O'Hagan%2C%20a%20lifelong%20athlete%20whose%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20spans%20Equinox%20and%20Nike%2C%20strength%20training%20was%20a%20major%20source%20of%20support%20at%20key%20moments%20throughout%20her%20career%2C%20including%20after%20the%20birth%20of%20her%20second%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20those%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-workout-3-hours-week-tips-sports-medicine-doctor-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehours%20in%20the%20gym%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20paid%20dividends%20in%20terms%20of%20energy%2C%20focus%2C%20and%20confidence%20at%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20I%20didn't%20feel%20like%20getting%20up%20and%20going%20to%20the%20gym%2C%20I%20knew%20that%20by%20the%20time%20I%20came%20home%2C%20it%20would%20give%20me%20that%20empowerment%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BHaving%20a%20strong%20body%20equates%20to%20a%20strong%20mind%2C%20equates%20to%20me%20being%20able%20to%20handle%20the%20big%20life%20that%20I%20want%20to%20have.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20tabindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20data-media-container%3D%5C%22image%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22img%5C%22%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-figure-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anne%20Marie%20Chaker%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d7eede05c9b303c4e76acd%3Fwidth%3D1300%26format%3Djpeg%26auto%3Dwebp%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%5Cn%3Cfigcaption%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-caption%5C%22%3E%5CnWomen%20can%2C%20and%20should%2C%20lift%20heavy.%20%3Cspan%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-source%5C%22%3E%5CnStella%20Kalinina%20for%20BI%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EFitting%20exercise%20into%20your%20day%20also%20highlights%20effective%20time%20management%20and%20multitasking%20skills.%20Chaker%20said%20it's%20a%20non-negotiable%20for%20her%2C%20even%20when%20she%20has%20to%20bring%20her%20laptop%20to%20the%20gym%20and%20take%20calls%20or%20answer%20emails%20between%20sets.%20She's%20seen%20other%20women%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20flex%20to%20show%20that%20this%20is%20something%20you%20prioritize.%20You%20can%20get%20it%20all%20done%2C%20and%20you%20can%20be%20strong%20and%20kick%20ass%2C%26quot%3B%20Chaker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20women%2C%20hitting%20the%20weights%20is%20an%20opportunity%20to%20own%20the%20room%2C%20take%20up%20space%20at%20the%20table%20literally%20and%20metaphorically%2C%20said%20Robb-O'Hagan.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we've%20seen%20a%20new%20era%20of%20execs%20focused%20on%20presenting%20their%20physiques%20as%20symbols%20of%20discipline%20and%20rigor%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjiu-jitsu-longevity-workout-middle-aged-men-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaking%20up%20jiu-jitsu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adopting%20high-protein%20diets%2C%20and%20practicing%20intermittent%20fasting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20you%20can%20do%20physically%20is%20such%20a%20wonderful%20metaphor%20for%20what%20you%20can%20do%20mentally%20and%20emotionally%20as%20a%20leader%20in%20the%20workplace%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20ultimately%20strength%20training%20is%20about%20self-efficacy%2C%20and%20that's%20really%20what%20leadership%20is%20about%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2258a6833c-ab8f-4194-ace6-e83e37979376%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHappy%20hour%20at%20the%20barbell%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELate%20last%20year%2C%20Chaker%20had%20the%20networking%20opportunity%20of%20a%20lifetime.%20At%20a%20women's%20leadership%20conference%20in%20Montana%2C%20Chaker%20ran%20into%20a%20top%20businesswoman%20%E2%80%94%20she%20wouldn't%20name-drop%20out%20of%20respect%20for%20her%20privacy%2C%20but%20she's%20one%20of%20the%20fewer%20than%20500%20women%20billionaires%20on%20the%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20started%20when%20she%20asked%20to%20borrow%20Chaker's%20resistance%20band%20during%20a%20chance%20meeting%20in%20the%20hotel%20gym.%20The%20impromptu%20one-on-one%20chat%20offered%20a%20more%20memorable%20moment%20of%20connection%20than%20any%20keynote%20speech%20or%20skill-sharing%20lunch%2C%20she%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLifting%20is%20a%20great%20equalizer%2C%26quot%3B%20Chaker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20tabindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20data-media-container%3D%5C%22image%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22img%5C%22%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-figure-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anne%20Marie%20Chaker%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d7efd396ef6a4c9d1215b7%3Fwidth%3D1300%26format%3Djpeg%26auto%3Dwebp%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%5Cn%3Cfigcaption%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-caption%5C%22%3E%5CnStrength%20training%20doesn't%20need%20to%20be%20complicated%20to%20be%20effective.%20A%20simple%20set%20of%20dumbbells%20is%20enough%20to%20build%20muscle%20and%20strength.%20%3Cspan%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-source%5C%22%3E%5CnStella%20Kalinina%20for%20BI%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Chaker%2C%20who%20became%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flift-weights-eat-more-how-to-transform-physique-40s-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebodybuilder%20in%20her%2040s%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20lifting%20not%20only%20provides%20her%20with%20unique%20and%20intimate%20networking%20opportunities%20but%20also%20benefits%20her%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20started%20lifting%2C%20everything%20in%20my%20life%20changed.%20I%20got%20a%20raise%20at%20work.%20I%20was%20interviewing%20better.%20My%20story%20ideas%20got%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Chaker%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it%20wasn't%20just%20because%20of%20cool%20muscles.%20It%20was%20because%20it%20changed%20my%20view%20of%20how%20I%20took%20up%20space%20in%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWomen%20aren't%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuilding-muscle-barbell-dumbbell-kettlebell-how-to-choose-which-one-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epumping%20iron%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20isolation.%20Boutique%20fitness%2C%20revitalized%20post-pandemic%2C%20has%20made%20health%20an%20elevated%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frun-club-hiit-class-networking-fitness-sweatworking-vcs-founders-lessons-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esocial%20event%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20prompting%20business%20leaders%20to%20move%20happy%20hour%20from%20the%20bar%20to%20the%20barbell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227279%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Deb%20stern%20and%20her%20trainer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d7ef9296ef6a4c9d1215ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225199%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBeyond%20the%20physical%20gains%2C%20lifting%20weights%20builds%20confidence%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20take%20up%20space%20and%20rise%20to%20a%20challenge%2C%20crucial%20assets%20for%20leadership%20roles.%3Cp%3ESydney%20Krantz%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20as%20more%20women%20are%20interested%20in%20the%20weight%20room%2C%20it%20can%20still%20retain%20an%20air%20of%20gymtimidation.%20For%20savvy%20fitness%20pros%2C%20that's%20created%20a%20prime%20audience%20for%20women-centered%20strength%20spaces%2C%20according%20to%20Larson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELarson%20opened%20her%20own%20gym%2C%20Tension%20Strength%2C%20in%20Brooklyn%20after%20years%20of%20coaching%20for%20Row%20House%20and%20other%20studios.%20She%20noticed%20a%20demographic%20of%20high-achieving%20women%20who%20wanted%20to%20level%20up%20their%20exercise%20beyond%20cardio%20and%20Pilates%2C%20but%20weren't%20sure%20where%20to%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrength%20training%2C%20by%20its%20nature%2C%20requires%20failure%20in%20order%20to%20grow.%20That%20translates%20well%20to%20an%20executive%20mindset%2C%20taking%20on%20challenges%20and%20setbacks%20to%20build%20back%20better%2C%20and%20gives%20women%20in%20particular%20a%20space%20to%20practice%20this%20skill%20without%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20a%20lot%20more%20conditioned%20to%20see%20men%20trying%20and%20failing%2C%20iterating%2C%20whereas%20with%20women%2C%20there's%20this%20expectation%20that%20we%20succeed%20the%20first%20time%20or%20we%20disappear%2C%26quot%3B%20Larson%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20strength%20training%2C%20confidence%20translates%20into%20all%20different%20areas%20of%20life%20because%20you%20understand%20it's%20safe%20to%20try.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photos%20of%20the%20winners%20of%20Ms.%20Olympia%2C%20female%20bodybuilding's%20most%20prestigious%20competition%2C%20from%201980%20to%20early%202000s%20adorn%20one%20of%20the%20walls%20at%20Gold's%20Gym%20in%20Venice%2C%20California%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d7ea8c96ef6a4c9d12156c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWeightlifting%20isn't%20a%20new%20phenomenon%20for%20women%2C%20but%20it's%20more%20popular%20than%20ever%20before%2C%20according%20to%20trainers.%3Cp%3EStella%20Kalinina%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESellers%2C%20the%20former%20Fortune%20editor%2C%20also%20sees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Filona-maher-simple-tip-get-enough-protein-without-obsessing-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewomen's%20fitness%20%3C%2Fa%3Eas%20a%20means%20to%20match%20the%20close-knit%2C%20exclusive%20clubs%20that%20powerful%20men%20have%20enjoyed%20for%20decades.%20In%201996%2C%20just%20one%20executive%20on%20the%20Fortune%20500%20was%20a%20woman.%20Today%2C%20they%20make%20up%2010%25%20%E2%80%94%20still%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go.%20Sellers%20hopes%20that%20connections%20built%20at%20the%20gyms%20could%20help%20close%20the%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20working%20really%20hard%20to%20create%20the%20female%20version%20of%20the%20golf%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20Sellers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwomen-lifting-weights-strength-training-career-leadership-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775901481000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d7f0ed96ef6a4c9d1215c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwomen-lifting-weights-strength-training-career-leadership-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20women%20are%20lifting%20weights%20and%20strength%20training.%20It's%20building%20skills%20and%20confidence%20that%20translate%20to%20career%20growth%20and%20executive%20roles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22glandsverk%40insider.com%20(Gabby%20Landsverk)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwomen-lifting-weights-strength-training-career-leadership-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uber%20and%20DoorDash%20have%20an%20identity%20theft%20problem%2C%20and%20it's%20costing%20people%20on%20tax%20day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20exits%20a%20compact%20Uber%20car%20while%20wearing%20a%20baseball%20cap%20and%20sunglasses%20at%20Los%20Angeles%20International%20Airport.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d6be771a512d0a63e73baf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Florida%20resident%20is%20suing%20Uber%20over%20the%20income%20it%20reported%20to%20the%20IRS%2C%20saying%20he%20never%20worked%20for%20the%20company.%3Cp%3EMyung%20J.%20Chun%20%2F%20Los%20Angeles%20Times%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Florida%20man%20who%20said%20he%20never%20worked%20for%20Uber%20said%20the%20app%20reported%20income%20in%20his%20name%20to%20the%20IRS.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20the%20man%20is%20suing%20the%20ride-hailing%20app.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20the%20latest%20example%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoordash-other-apps-using-gig-workers-collect-data-ai-stores-2026-3%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUber%20and%20other%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E%20struggling%20to%20verify%20who%20is%20on%20their%20platforms.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20and%20DoorDash%20are%20telling%20the%20Internal%20Revenue%20Service%20that%20some%20people%20earned%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20on%20their%20platforms%20%E2%80%94%20though%20the%20people%20say%20they%20never%20worked%20for%20the%20apps%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20individual%20is%20taking%20his%20claims%20to%20court.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDamian%20Josefsberg%20alleged%20that%20Uber%20reported%20over%20%241%2C200%20in%20earnings%20in%20his%20name%20to%20the%20IRS%20for%202021%20tax%20year%2C%20in%20a%20complaint%20filed%20in%20a%20Florida%20court%20last%20month.%20Josefsberg%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Florida%20and%20runs%20a%20laser%20alignment%20company%2C%20has%20never%20worked%20for%20the%20app%2C%20Kenneth%20Dante%20Murena%2C%20his%20attorney%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20is%20seeking%20class-action%20status%2C%20which%20would%20add%20plaintiffs%20with%20similar%20experiences%20to%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Uber%20spokesperson%20confirmed%20that%20Josefsberg%20never%20worked%20for%20the%20app%20and%20directed%20Business%20Insider%20to%20a%20form%20on%20its%20website%20titled%20%26quot%3B1099%20delivery%20error%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20asks%20people%20to%20submit%20erroneous%20tax%20forms%2C%20a%20picture%20of%20their%20government%20ID%2C%20a%20selfie%20with%20their%20ID%2C%20and%20a%20police%20report%20so%20Uber%20can%20investigate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJosefsberg's%20experience%20points%20to%20a%20problem%20Uber%20and%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-spark-delivery-app-multiple-accounts-names-verify-identity-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egig-work%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20faced%20for%20years%3A%20the%20people%20who%20drive%20passengers%20or%20deliver%20food%20aren't%20always%20who%20they%20say%20they%20are%2C%20and%20some%20have%20bought%20accounts%20on%20illegal%20markets%20rather%20than%20getting%20proper%20access%20by%20signing%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20apps%20have%20responded%20with%20new%20verification%20efforts%2C%20such%20as%20asking%20workers%20to%20regularly%20submit%20selfies%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-spark-delivery-drivers-prove-identity-in-person-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eto%20show%20up%20in%20person%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20verify%20their%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2208779fa8-14e8-4601-a206-f8e26499f0ae%5C%22%3EUber%20has%20issues%20with%20ID%20verification%2C%20safety%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20says%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EApps%20like%20Uber%20have%20added%20millions%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-uber-lyft-doordash-gig-workers-per-hour-2025-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egig%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20their%20platforms%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20and%20a%20half%2C%20and%20Josefsberg's%20lawsuit%20alleges%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUber%20isn't%20doing%20enough%20to%20verify%20those%20workers'%20identities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BScreening%20barriers%20such%20as%20'clean'%20background%20checks%2C%20issue-free%20driving%20records%2C%20or%20the%20ability%20to%20work%20legally%20in%20the%20United%20States%20impede%20Uber's%20abilities%20to%20rapidly%20increase%20its%20driver%20pool%20and%20thus%20its%20trip%20deliveries%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Uber%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company%20disagrees%20with%20the%20claims%20in%20Josefsberg's%20lawsuit.%20The%20company%20%26quot%3Bmaintains%20robust%20safeguards%20designed%20to%20detect%20and%20prevent%20fraudulent%20activity%2C%20and%20we%20continually%20enhance%20these%20systems%20to%20address%20emerging%20tactics%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20also%20said%20that%20it%20conducts%20background%20checks%20on%20drivers%2C%20including%20reviews%20of%20their%20driving%20and%20criminal%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrivers%20whose%20real%20identities%20and%20backgrounds%20are%20unknown%20pose%20a%20safety%20risk%20to%20passengers%2C%20Murena%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20is%20facing%20multiple%20lawsuits%20that%20allege%20the%20company%20is%20liable%20for%20sexual%20misconduct%2C%20including%20rape%2C%20by%20its%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20public%20at%20large%20would%20like%20to%20know%20that%20Uber%20is%20confirming%20that%20the%20drivers%20are%20who%20they%20say%20they%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20Murena%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJosefsberg's%20lawsuit%20seeks%20damages%20from%20Uber%20and%20a%20correction%20to%20his%20tax%20record%2C%20because%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20company%20reported%20the%20income%20to%20the%20IRS%20under%20his%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMurena%20said%20he's%20received%20roughly%20two%20dozen%20calls%20from%20others%20who%20also%20received%201099s%20from%20Uber%20despite%20saying%20they've%20never%20worked%20for%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222fdfc533-8a18-4fb2-a419-fef57c95143f%5C%22%3EDoorDash%20reported%20%2424%2C000%20in%20income%20for%20one%20worker%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-it-gig-work-side-hustle-full-time-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eride-hailing%20and%20delivery%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20faced%20similar%20is