0even%20if%20equity%20prices%20continue%20to%20rise%2C%20as%20some%20of%20the%20forces%20that%20pushed%20equity%20volatility%20higher%20in%20the%20late%201990s%20as%20the%20tech%20investment%20boom%20matured%20come%20increasingly%20into%20play.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman's%20strategists%20reexamined%20the%20models%20they%20use%20to%20forecast%20stock%20volatility%2C%20updating%20their%20forecasts%20for%20longer-term%20volatility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bobvious%26quot%3B%20route%20to%20higher%20stock%20market%20volatility%20is%20cyclical%20economic%20deterioration%2C%20they%20say%2C%20though%20they%20explained%20that%20there%20are%20other%20underlying%20structural%20forces%20contributing%20to%20their%20outlook%20for%20a%20longer%20period%20of%20volatility.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModels%20of%20the%20macro%20and%20market%20drivers%20of%20equity%20volatility%20suggest%20that%20longer-dated%20implied%20volatility%20'should'%20have%20been%20rising%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20driven%20largely%20by%20rising%20equity%20market%20concentration%20and%20a%20slowly%20rising%20unemployment%20rate%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bank%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20the%20Iran%20war%2C%20the%20two%20biggest%20drivers%20of%20a%20swingier%20stock%20market%20will%20be%20higher%20market%20concentration%20and%20higher%20unemployment%2C%20in%20Goldman's%20view.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ecf7cf4d-1d56-4939-bcd6-fcf077fe3fe7%5C%22%3EAI-driven%20market%20concentration%20sets%20up%20stock%20volatility%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20has%20fueled%20the%20stock%20market's%20bull%20run%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%20as%20investors%20pile%20into%20the%20emerging%20tech%2C%20a%20backdrop%20that%20sets%20up%20equities%20for%20more%20volatility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20the%20concentration%20of%20value%20in%20AI-related%20areas%20of%20the%20market%20adds%20to%20the%20risk%20of%20higher%20volatility%20over%20time%20as%20focus%20increases%20on%20whether%20the%2